# Title: Hidden Local User Creation
# Author: Christian Burkard (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2021-05-03
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the creation of a local hidden user account which should not happen for event ID 4720.
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.t1136.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/win_security_hidden_user_creation.yml

EventID=4720 TargetUserName="*$" NOT TargetUserName="HomeGroupUser$"